steps.name: I am on Radio me module
I signed in from benefits page
I click on the "Programme Updates" tab

description text "Newly available episodes (most recent first) of the last 100 programmes you added to your favourites. Removing an item means you’ll stop getting new episodes of that programme here." should be displayed at the top

arguments.val: Newly available episodes (most recent first) of the last 100 programmes you added to your favourites. Removing an item means you’ll stop getting new episodes of that programme here.

steps.name: I am on Radio me module
I signed in from benefits page
I click on the "Episodes & Clips" tab
description text "Clips and individual episodes you’ve added to your Favourites. Any newly available episodes of these programmes will appear in Programme Updates." should be displayed at the top

arguments.val: Clips and individual episodes you’ve added to your Favourites. Any newly available episodes of these programmes will appear in Programme Updates.
